import React from 'react';
import { FormGroup, Label, Input, StyledTextarea, SignupContainer, FormButton, ContactH1} from "./SignupElements";

const handleSubmit = e => {
    e.preventDefault();
    console.log("Succeeded!!!")
  };

const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <SignupContainer id='contact'>
    <ContactH1>Contact Us</ContactH1>
    <FormGroup>
      <Label htmlFor="label">Name</Label>
      <Input id="label" />
      <Label>Email Address</Label>
      <Input />
      <Label>Phone</Label>
      <Input />
      <Label>State</Label>
      <Input />
      <Label>City</Label>
      <Input />
      <Label>Equipment</Label>
      <select id="job" name="field4">
        <optgroup label="Trucks">
        <option value="18wheeler">18 wheeler</option>
        <option value="flatBed">Flat Bed</option>
        <option value="boxTruck">Box Truck</option>
        <option value="other_indoor">Other</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="Vans">
        <option value="53DryVan">53' Dry Van</option>
        <option value="53Reefer">53' Reefer</option>
        </optgroup>
        </select>      
    </FormGroup>
    <FormGroup>
    <Label>Subject</Label>
      <Input />
    <Label>Message:</Label>
    <StyledTextarea placeholder="Please enter your inquiry here"></StyledTextarea>
    </FormGroup>
    <FormButton onClick="handleSubmit()">Send Message</FormButton>
    <button onClick="handleSubmit()">Click me</button>
    </SignupContainer>
        
  );
};

export default Signup;
